quran[22{c,v,t}:
54,50,aur hamara hukum bas aik hi hukum hota hai aur palak jhupkatay woh amal mein aa jata hai
54,51,"tum jaisay bohat soon ko hum halaak kar chuke hain, phir hai koi nasiyaat qubool karne wala ?"
54,52,jo kuch unhon ne kya hai woh sab dftron mein darj hai
54,53,aur har choti barri baat likhi hui mojood hai
54,54,nafarmani se parhaiz karne walay yaqeenan baghoon aur nﮦron mein hon ge
54,55,"sachhi izzat ki jagah, barray Zee Iqtidaar badshah ke qareeb"
55,1,rehman ne
55,2,iss quran ki taleem di hai
55,3,usi ne ensaan ko peda kya
55,4,aur usay bolna sikhaya
55,5,Sooraj aur chaand aik hisaab ke paband hain
55,6,aur tarre aur darakht sab sajda raiz hain
55,7,aasman ko uss ne buland kya aur maizaan qaim kar di
55,8,iss ka taqaza yeh hai ke tum maizaan mein khlal nah daalo
55,9,insaaf ke sath theek theek tolo aur traazo mein dandi nah maro
55,10,zameen ko is ne sab makhloqaat ke liye banaya
55,11,is mein har terhan ke bakasrat lazeez phal hain khajoor ke darakht hain jin ke phal ghlafon mein liptay hue hain
55,12,terhan terhan ke ghallay hain jin mein bhosa bhi hota hai aur dana bhi
55,13,"pas ae jin o ans, tum apne rab ki kin kin nematon ko jhutlao ge ?"
55,14,ensaan ko uss ne theekri jaisay sokhey srhe hue gaaray se banaya
55,15,aur jin ko aag ki lapat se peda kya
55,16,"pas ae jin o ans, tum apne rab ke kin kin ajaaeb qudrat ko jhutlao ge ?"
